    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-09-01T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-09-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="123" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d123">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Denby</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Jernigan.</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-09-01">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">September</hi> 1,
                                    1894</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department instructs me that you had no power to receive, and are not
                            authorized to hold, the alleged spies. Deliver to Taotai.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Denby.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
